metadata.name: RUBBER FLASH
metadata.description: Tattoo Flash and 1930's Rubber hose Cartoons: A Reflection on Artistic Influences" is a thoughtfully crafted art piece that pays homage to two distinct art forms. Inspired by the bold designs of tattoo flash and the iconic style of 1930's rubber hose cartoons, this piece explores the ways in which these art forms have shaped and influenced my art. Featuring a cast of strange characters this piece invites viewers to consider the enduring impact of traditional tattoo art and vintage animation on modern artistic expression. It is a tribute to the timeless beauty and enduring influence of these art forms.
